                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410405-1267-offence-1 t18410405-cd-230"></join>31st of March</rs>, 21bs. weight of marjoram seed, value 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18410405-name-1452" type="victimName">
